  "reference_number": "RUS2639",
  "remarks": "\nThe Secretary of State considers that there are reasonable grounds to suspect that John Michael ORMEROD has been involved in obtaining a benefit from or supporting the Government of Russia by owning or controlling directly or indirectly, or working as a director (whether executive or non-executive) of, a person, other than an individual, carrying on business in a sector of strategic significance to the Government of Russia, namely the Russian energy sector.  \n",
